quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  100,1,By the snorting CHARGERS
  100,2,And those that dash off sparks of fire
  100,3,And those that scour to the attack at morn
  100,4,And stir therein the dust aloft
  100,5,And cleave therein their midway through a host
  100,6,"Truly, Man is to his Lord ungrateful"
  100,7,And of this he is himself a witness
  100,8,"And truly, he is vehement in the love of this world's good"
  100,9,"Ah! knoweth he not, that when that which is in the graves shall be laid bare"
  100,10,And that which is in men's breasts shall be brought forth
  100,11,Verily their Lord shall on that day be informed concerning them